---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Track packages and deliveries detected in your mail

Usage: mxr deliveries [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list     List tracked deliveries (default)
  get      Show one delivery, including its source messages
  resolve  Mark a delivery delivered/done (leaves the active list)
  dismiss  Hide a delivery (false positive)
  scan     Re-scan recent mail for deliveries
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
